core":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:12:37.000Z","msg":"標準連登答案：除左港大之後其他大學都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主都唔洗咁介意既 相比其他地方台灣阿韓國阿個d 百幾間大學 入大學率80幾90%<br />\n香港入大學率都幾低 仲要得十零間到（計埋專上學院）<br />\n入到大學都叻架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a15822a2d15e8c299341ee48ffce37606d18b0b","tid":324902,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標準連登答案：除左港大之<span style=\"color: red;\">外</span>其他大學都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主都唔洗咁介意既 相比其他地方台灣阿韓國阿個d 百幾間大學 入大學率80幾90%<br />\n香港入大學率都幾低 仲要得十零間到（計埋專上學院）<br />\n入到大學都叻架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4f20d5446901f18a92efafe5f4930549a77b22f9","tid":324902,"uid":107382,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:18:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>社會大學先係真正嘅挑戰，巴打加油!</blockquote><br />\n多誰你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c0140b7055567a47c022f7a44883211093c5df","tid":324902,"uid":107382,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>社會大學先係真正嘅挑戰，巴打加油!</blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4fbe0dc32458d87737b6cfbc81c98aeeb8edfa4d","tid":324902,"uid":107382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你咩 你估入到就大撚哂？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁慚愧咪撚讀囉 咁撚睇唔起ou當初做乜interview?<br />\n你當自己入到就一定畢到業？ <br />\n年中大把人grad唔到 樓主應該係其中一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n突然咁惡做咩啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能佢係ou同學？唔使咁大反應既，沒有對比就沒有傷害，當身邊人個個讀書叻既時候自然會感到自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gi